    "description": "K Raheja Corp South Asia Partners has an exciting opening for a Property Consultant at our Vijayawada office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout K Raheja Corp South Asia Partners:\nK Raheja Corp South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Provide advisory services on property investment and market trends\n• Achieve monthly and quarterly sales targets\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in Title Search\n• Proficiency in Investment Analysis\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with K Raheja Corp South Asia Partners!",
